    {
        "source_sentence": "田中多見牛跡。",
        "from": "X64n1271_001:0785a24_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": ")　堤回陌轉向溪西　　一路深蹄間淺蹄　端的新知尋舊識　　人牛到此兩無迷見牛(白牛穩臥田中。",
        "from": "X64n1271_001:0785a24_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "童子遙見歡喜。",
        "from": "X64n1271_001:0785b03_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": ")　行盡山村過水村　　草中忽見白牛蹲　欣欣穩步方輕快　　喘息初調與細論得牛(白牛從容起立。",
        "from": "X64n1271_001:0785b03_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "童子喜撫其背。",
        "from": "X64n1271_001:0785b06_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": ")　跋涉溪山豈憚勞　　白牛頓獲價彌高　快心久別重相契　　善撫從容喜伏弢護牛(童子閒坐石上。",
        "from": "X64n1271_001:0785b06_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "白牛飲澗自適。",
        "from": "X64n1271_001:0785b09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": ")　牛適人閒却瘦肥　　風清月白久忘飢　幽香野綠盈山谷　　幾度朝暉映夕暉騎歸(夕陽在山。",
        "from": "X64n1271_001:0785b09_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "白牛歸宿。",
        "from": "X64n1271_001:0785b12_15",
