    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "童跨牛背。",
        "from": "X64n1271_001:0785b12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "吹笛自樂。",
        "from": "X64n1271_001:0785b12_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": ")　放曠騎歸世所稀　　柳絲鞭影任風揮　山童吹徹無生曲　　笛韻餘暉入禁闈忘牛(明月在天。",
        "from": "X64n1271_001:0785b12_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
